Title: A journey to find a real love
DateModified: '2018-02-28'
DatePublished: '2018-04-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2018/applications/a-journey-to-find-a-real-love
SetInCountry: Indonesia
Category: The last thing I expected
AuthorName: Syafiani Afwadi
AuthorCountry: Indonesia
Text: "Lhokseumawe\n\n\"A special journey not only must to hold pasport and flying\
  \ with airplane. Because each journey have any own mean\" \n\nDo not go to far away.\
  \ Stay on near place for the first\n\nToday, my heart journey bring me to a  place\
  \ not so far with my address. Only sent about 30 minutes to reach its place. A high\
  \ place where you can see a scenery or to look the treasure that was lost.\nA new\
  \ area with name \"goa Jepang\" in bahasa Indonesia mean \"Japan Cave\" on English.\
  \ A place was belong time ago as an evidence of histrory. \n\nThe location of this\
  \ place is 100 mters on the sea. The loval community call this place as \" Goa Jepang/Japan\
  \ Cave\" but the government of Lhokseumawe regency call \"Taman Ngingetin  Jioh\"\
  \ on Aceh language or \"a Park to see  the future\" on English. \n\n\nIf you want\
  \ to come to this place of tourism , the exactly location at nasional Street Medan\
  \ -  Banda Aceh.  When you are on Blang Panyang village or in the Grave of Hero\
  \ park, please turn right, that climb on the little hill. In that hill that Japan\
  \ Cave be there.   \n\nPlease look forward as you can\n\nThus, not only that i want\
  \ to tell but I wanna tell you about \"taman melihat jauh\" or \"a Park to see future,\
  \ so you see that the creator from the God that put love on the earth. And i also,\
  \ here I can see my future  on my begin journey to find my love where I don't know\
  \ him\n\n\n\"Taman melihat jauh or a Park to see the future\"\nMy feeling?? Oh no.\
  \ I am really could not to explain that love to a country can Made a histrory place\
  \  like this. Will be a feeling a journey Will get the retort? Because when you\
  \ see far away ia a solution. That a jouney still long. Many of part is waiting\
  \ to get a love. See far away ia a retort for long waiting. That irlt has something\
  \ have to catch. Maybe the love. Is waiting in someplace and waiting for pikiranku\
  \ iya up to back? \n\nAh, love will make everything possible.\n\nI see around and\
  \ far away on the sea view. Nothing a beiatiful scenery except the blue of sea.\
  \ Close your eyes  and feel of India blow. Open your eyes   and see far  as you\
  \ can, take a journey as far as you can. Maybe  your love  is  waiting  and trapping\
  \ among a thousand Park ini the world.  Let's keep spirit to find a love and prepare\
  \ my next journey!\n\nAcross it you Will find  love. Make your eye seduced and your\
  \ feet start  itch. Ask to going far away as I can to take and found a real    \
  \  love actually it jas been.  See as far as you and   because there still kept\
  \   of your love."
